---
title: Easy Creole-Style Beef & BBQ Slaw with Sweetcorn Rice & Yoghurt
description: Dig into an easy bowl of Creole-inspired delights! From tender and mildly spiced beef strips to sweetcorn-studded rice and
crunchy slaw, this colourful meal gets a creamy dollop of yoghurt to bring the whole flavoursome feast together, and in only
25 minutes!
